  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个数据迁移的流程图。场景是从本地PostgreSQL数据库迁移到Azure上的托管服务，中间用DMS做迁移工具。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremDB",
        "AzureDB",
        "DMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个数据库节点，中间是DMS迁移链路。左侧的本地库需要标注成PostgreSQL吗？右侧Azure端要显示具体产品名称吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremDB",
        "AzureDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，左侧写PostgreSQL就行，右侧要完整一点，写成Azure Database for PostgreSQL。DMS作为连接线上的标签，表示迁移服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremDB",
        "AzureDB",
        "DMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了。左边是圆柱形的PostgreSQL节点，右边是Azure Database for PostgreSQL，中间箭头标注DMS。方向是从上到下排列，符合TB布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremDB",
        "AzureDB",
        "DMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "方向能不能确认一下？TB是从上到下吧？我想让数据流向清晰一些，从本地到云端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremDB",
        "AzureDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，TB就是Top-Bottom，本地PostgreSQL在上，Azure Database for PostgreSQL在下，箭头向下，符合数据从本地迁移到云端的流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremDB",
        "AzureDB",
        "DMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以了。不过节点形状上，两个数据库都用圆柱形表示存储，这样比较规范。DMS不用单独画节点，就放在连接线上作为迁移服务的标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremDB",
        "AzureDB",
        "DMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整完成。两个数据库节点都是圆柱形，连接线上标注DMS，整体采用从上到下的流向布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnPremDB",
        "AzureDB",
        "DMS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
